messages.message: I saw that if I’m logged out on dogfood, I have to manually navigate to dogfood.instabase.com/account/login (http://dogfood.instabase.com/account/login) to login (b/c about.instabse.com (http://about.instabse.com) links to instabase.com (http://instabase.com) not dogfood.instabase.com (http://dogfood.instabase.com)). Is that going to cause any issues with our deployment? Just checking if it’s a bug @Jessica @Ashish
It's by design from the day of our launch.
